  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    EU citizens in the UK: access to social housing and homelessness assistance in a no deal scenario
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph ">
    Information for local housing authorities on the rights of EU citizens in the UK to access social housing, including supported housing, and homelessness assistance if the UK leaves the EU without a deal.
  </p>

  </div>
</div>

